# Cloudflare Pages — redirects
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
# (CF Pages already serves /404.html for unmatched routes automatically.)

# Legacy WordPress slugs → new routes
# NOTE: do NOT add a "/our-services/  /our-services" rule. Cloudflare Pages serves
# directory pages at their trailing-slash URL, so stripping the slash here creates
# an infinite redirect loop (the browser shows "this page isn't working").
/contacts        /contact         301
/contacts/       /contact         301
/portfolio-category/*  /portfolio  301
